<Layout title="AI Won't Replace Developers — But It Will Redefine Them" description="Why boomerang hiring, code review bottlenecks, and the real productivity equation prove that AI augments developers rather than replacing them">
  <nav class="breadcrumb">
    <a href="/blog">Articles</a>
    <span class="breadcrumb-sep">→</span>
    <span class="breadcrumb-current">Technology</span>
  </nav>

